data.title: Justin Moore
data.meta_description: Justin Moore. Soundtrack: Collateral Terror - Battle for America. Justin Moore was born on 30 March 1984 in Arkansas, USA. He is a music artist and actor, known for Collateral Terror - Battle for America (2017), Justin Moore: Lettin' the Night Roll (2013) and Justin Moore: How I Got to Be This Way (2010). He has been married to Kate Moore since 2007. They have three children.
